# Generative Text Model

## 📌 Overview
This project is part of my internship task. It is a **Generative Text Model** built using GPT-2 from Hugging Face Transformers.  
The tool generates coherent paragraphs based on user prompts.

## 🚀 How to Run
1. Place this project folder in VS Code.
2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
